#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:16
msgid "GCompris"
msgstr "GCompris"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:17
msgid "Educational game for children"
msgstr "Izglītojoša spēle bērniem"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:19
msgid ""
"GCompris is a high quality educational software suite, including a large "
"number of activities for children aged 2 to 10."
msgstr ""
"„GCompris“ ir kvalitatīvu izglītojošu spēļu komplekts, kas satur dažādas "
"nodarbības bērniem no divu līdz desmit gadu vecumam."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:20
msgid ""
"Some of the activities are game orientated, but nonetheless still "
"educational."
msgstr ""
"Dažas aktivitātes ir veidotas kā spēles, bet tās tāpat ir izglītojošas."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:22
msgid ""
"Below you can find a list of categories with some of the activities "
"available in that category."
msgstr ""
"Šis ir saraksts ar dažām attiecīgajās kategorijās atrodamajām aktivitātēm."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:25
msgid "computer discovery: keyboard, mouse, different mouse gestures, etc."
msgstr "dators: tastatūra, pele, dažādi žesti ar peli u.c."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:26
msgid ""
"arithmetic: table memory, enumeration, mirror image, balance the scale, "
"change giving, etc."
msgstr ""
"aritmētika: atmiņas tabula, skaitīšana, spoguļattēls, svaru līdzsvarošana, "
"atlikuma izdošana u.c."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:28
msgid "science: the canal lock, color mixing, gravity concept, etc."
msgstr "zinātne: kanāla slūžas, krāsu jaukšana, gravitācija u.c."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:29
msgid "games: memory, connect 4, tic tac toe, sudoku, hanoi tower, etc."
msgstr ""
"spēles: atmiņa, četri rindā, krustiņi un nullītes, sudoku, Hanojas tornis u."
"c."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:30
msgid "reading: reading practice, etc."
msgstr "lasīšana: lasīšanas vingrinājumi u.c."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:31
msgid ""
"other: learn to tell time, the braille system, maze, music instruments, etc."
msgstr ""
"citas: pateikt laiku, Braila raksts, labirints, mūzikas instrumenti u.c."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:34
msgid ""
"Currently GCompris offers in excess of 100 activities and more are being "
"developed. GCompris is free software, that means that you can adapt it to "
"your own needs, improve it and, most importantly, share it with children "
"everywhere."
msgstr ""
"Šobrīd „GCompris“ piedāvā vairāk nekā 100 aktivitāšu un to skaits aug. "
"„GCompris“ ir brīvā programmatūra — tas nozīmē, ka vari to pielāgot savām "
"vajadzībām, uzlabot un, protams, dalīties ar bērniem visā pasaulē!"

